repository-code: "https://github.com/jae7cho/fmri-repro-agent"
abstract: >-
  An LLM-based agentic tool that ingests a published fMRI research paper
  (PDF) and emits a ready-to-run replication package — BIDS metadata,
  fMRIPrep pipeline configuration, BIDS Stats Models JSON, container
  specifications, and Slurm submission scripts. Each output is accompanied
  by an explicit confidence and missingness report distinguishing stated,
  inferred, and unresolved parameters.
